metadata.name: Milky Way at Twilight
metadata.description:
I love to capture the milky way at twilight since this allows me to capture enough detail from both the galactic core as well as the surroundings. I have always been fascinated by the night sky and when I learned photography, I was immediately hooked to astrophotography

Artist: John Kimwell Laluma
Edition: 1/1 NFT
Location of Photograph: Kabankalan, Negros Occidental, Philippines.
